text: Alie Coumans-Zijlmans (born 24 March 1948) is a Dutch cyclist. She competed at the 1965 Netherlands Championship Road Race, finishing third. 1964 Gorinchem road race, finishing first, and 1965 Papendal road race finishing first. == References == Category:1948 births Category:Dutch cyclists Category:Living people
title: Alie Zijlmans
